CAPTURE MODULE

Hands-free, conversational capture

Record tasks and observations as you work.

Technicians can record steps, faults and observations as they work. FieldPal automatically structures and tags every entry to the correct asset or task turning daily activity into usable operational knowledge.

  • Captures work even in noisy environments
  • Auto-tags entries to assets and tasks
  • Cuts down paperwork and manual reporting
  • Keeps field data accurate and audit-ready

FAQs

Understanding FieldPal.ai .

What is FieldPal.ai?

FieldPal.ai is an AI-driven platform that converts complex operational documentation into searchable, bite-sized knowledge for frontline and field workers, enabling faster troubleshooting and safer operations.

Who uses FieldPal.ai?

Organisations with field-facing operations manufacturing, utilities, facilities management, large equipment service and inspection teams that need quick access to technical knowledge and standard operating procedures.

What problems does FieldPal.ai solve?

It reduces asset downtime, captures tribal expertise, unifies fragmented documentation and helps teams meet compliance and safety requirements by surfacing the right information at the right time.

How does FieldPal.ai work with our existing systems?

FieldPal.ai is API-first and supports integration with legacy systems, document stores and ERPs so you can embed knowledge into current workflows and apps. For developer resources, request API docs via our contact form.

Is FieldPal.ai secure and enterprise-grade?

Yes FieldPal.ai is designed for enterprise deployment with access controls and enterprise security features. For specific compliance, certification and data residency requirements, speak to the FieldPal team.

Can field workers use FieldPal.ai offline?

FieldPal.ai supports mobile-first workflows; discuss offline caching and sync options with the implementation team to ensure knowledge is available where connectivity is limited.

How long does implementation take?

Implementation time depends on scale and source data complexity. A typical pilot (ingesting a subset of documents and integrating one system) can be scoped within a few weeks liaise with FieldPal for a tailored timeline.

How is FieldPal.ai priced?

Pricing varies by number of users, integrations and level of customisation. Contact sales for a demo and tailored quote.

What support and onboarding do you offer?

Onboarding includes implementation support, admin training and access to developer documentation. Ongoing support packages are available see the Support page or contact the team.
